---
import { Search, Lightbulb, Rocket, BarChart } from 'lucide-react';
---

<section id="metodologia" class="w-full bg-gray-50 py-16 sm:py-24 lg:py-32">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    
    <div class="text-center mb-12 sm:mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-black mb-4">
        Nuestra <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-blue-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent" style="font-family: var(--font-secondary)">metodología</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Un proceso probado que transforma ideas en resultados tangibles y medibles.
      </p>
    </div>

    {/* Timeline Horizontal */}
    <div class="relative">
      {/* Línea horizontal - visible solo en desktop */}
      <div class="hidden lg:block absolute left-0 right-0 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 via-blue-600 via-orange-500 to-purple-600" style="top: 2.5rem;"></div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 lg:gap-6 relative z-10">
        
        {/* Paso 1 */}
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center h-full">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-600 to-purple-700 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 shadow-xl border-4 border-white flex-shrink-0">
            <Search className="w-10 h-10 text-white" />
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md border-2 border-purple-200 hover:border-purple-600 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 w-full cursor-pointer flex flex-col h-full">
            <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-black mb-2">1. Investigación</h3>
            <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed flex-grow">
              Analizamos tu mercado, competencia y audiencia para identificar oportunidades clave.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Paso 2 */}
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center h-full">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-blue-700 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 shadow-xl border-4 border-white flex-shrink-0">
            <Lightbulb className="w-10 h-10 text-white" />
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md border-2 border-blue-200 hover:border-blue-600 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 w-full cursor-pointer flex flex-col h-full">
            <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-black mb-2">2. Estrategia</h3>
            <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed flex-grow">
              Diseñamos un plan de acción personalizado con objetivos claros y medibles.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Paso 3 */}
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center h-full">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 shadow-xl border-4 border-white flex-shrink-0" style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, var(--color-hype-orange), #ff9500)">
            <Rocket className="w-10 h-10 text-white" />
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md border-2 border-orange-200 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 w-full cursor-pointer flex flex-col h-full" style="border-color: #ffb366;">
            <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-black mb-2">3. Ejecución</h3>
            <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed flex-grow">
              Implementamos las tácticas con precisión de tiburón: rápido, eficaz y sin errores.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Paso 4 */}
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center h-full">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-600 to-purple-700 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 shadow-xl border-4 border-white flex-shrink-0">
            <BarChart className="w-10 h-10 text-white" />
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md border-2 border-purple-200 hover:border-purple-600 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 w-full cursor-pointer flex flex-col h-full">
            <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-black mb-2">4. Optimización</h3>
            <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed flex-grow">
              Monitoreamos, analizamos y ajustamos constantemente para maximizar resultados.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

